Title: Goldstone Bosons in the Gaussian Approximation
Authors: Anna Okopi\'nska
Comments: 7 pages, Latex
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B375 (1996) 213-216
\\
  The O(N) symmetric scalar quantum field theory with \lambda\Phi^4 interaction
is discussed in the Gaussian approximation. It is shown that the Goldstone
theorem is fulfilled for arbitrary N.
